            "product_url": "https://www.amazon.com/dp/B08JJMJ8JB?tag=wbcmb-20",
            "product_rating_description": "<p>The EVMT brand was founded by professional athletes of varying disciplines. Apart from the basic liquid chalk, their options range from regular liquid chalk to sports-specific choices, including weightlifting, rock climbing, and dancing.</p><ul><li><strong>Ingredients:</strong> Magnesium Carbonate, liquid solution</li><li><strong>Smell:</strong> Lemon</li><li><strong>Drying Period:</strong> ~15 seconds</li><li><strong>Longevity:</strong> Moderate</li><li><strong>Fitness Category:</strong> Regular, weightlifting, rock climbing, dancing.</li><li><strong>Viscosity:</strong> Medium</li><li><strong>Color:</strong> White</li><li><strong>Price:</strong> $$</li></ul>",
            "product_rating_1": "5",
