        "product_E9HNYA": {
          "type": "product",
          "settings": {
            "product_title": "Friction Labs Quick Grip Secret Stuff Liquid Chalk",
            "short_product_title": "Friction Labs",
            "product_position": "4",
            "product_award": "",
            "product_url": "https://www.amazon.com/dp/B07S2TK63Y?tag=wbcmb-20",
            "product_rating_description": "<p>Friction Labs positions itself as a premium hand chalk brand. The company started in rock climbing but has since expanded its formula to other sports. It’s a bit harder to recommend due to a single bottle size and a bit higher price, but if you don’t mind the cost, it’s an excellent choice.</p><ul><li><strong>Ingredients:</strong> Magnesium Carbonate, liquid solution or alcohol (depending on the version)</li><li><strong>Smell:</strong> None</li><li><strong>Drying Period:</strong> ~20 seconds (alcohol-based), 60-90 sec (alcohol-free)</li><li><strong>Longevity:</strong> High</li><li><strong>Fitness Category:</strong> Weightlifting, Climbing, Gymnastics, Aerial arts, Racket/Batting sports</li><li><strong>Viscosity:</strong> High</li><li><strong>Color:</strong> White</li><li><strong>Price:</strong> $$$</li></ul>",
            "product_rating_1": "4.25",
            "product_rating_2": "5",
