            "product_rating_description": "<p>Next up, we have the Liquid Grip. This chalk advertises itself as an all-around great choice, so let’s see how good it is.</p><ul><li><strong>Ingredients:</strong> Magnesium Carbonate, alcohol, thickener, fragrance</li><li><strong>Smell:</strong> Coconut</li><li><strong>Drying Period:</strong> ~10-15 seconds</li><li><strong>Longevity:</strong> Moderate</li><li><strong>Fitness Category:</strong> Gymnastics, aerial arts, sports</li><li><strong>Viscosity:</strong> Medium</li><li><strong>Color:</strong> White</li><li><strong>Price:</strong> $</li></ul>",
